query:
SELECT 
  p.code,
  p.name,
  SUM(s.quantity) as total_vendido
FROM sales s
JOIN products p ON s.productId = p.id
WHERE s.saleDate >= '2025-09-01'
  AND s.saleDate < '2025-10-01'
GROUP BY p.id, p.code, p.name
ORDER BY total_vendido DESC
LIMIT 10
